text: Lukáš Fabiš (born 5 May 1998) is a Slovak footballer who plays for Nitra as a defender. ==Club career== ===FC Nitra=== Fabiš made his Fortuna Liga debut for Nitra against Senica on 18 November 2017. Fabiš played 90 minutes of the goal- less game.FC Nitra - FK Senica 0:0 18.11.2017, futbalnet.sk ==References== ==External links== * FC Nitra official club profile * * Futbalnet profile * Fortuna Liga profile Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Nitra Category:Slovak footballers Category:Slovakia under-21 international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:FC Nitra players Category:Slovak Super Liga players
